{
  "id": "adv_card_rio_03_01",
  "title": "神崎莉央 1話 大人げない自分",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――年が明けてから、数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Few days after new year",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "LizNoirは正月休みを返上し、特訓に励んでいた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "LizNoir canceled their New Year's break and now working on special training.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ、はぁ……ダメよ、こんなんじゃ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa‚ haa‚ haa… It's no good like this…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "みんな！　今のところ、もう一回よ\n出来るまで、何度でもやるわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone! Let's do it again from the top.\nWe'll do it as many times as it takes!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さん、ストップストップ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio-san‚ stop‚ stop!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "貴方……いつから来てたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You… When did you arrive?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "もう一時間以上前からですよ\n新年の挨拶をしても気がついてくれなかったけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've been here for over an hour.\nI greeted you for the New Year‚ but you didn't notice.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そう……ごめんなさい\n……でも、今はレッスンを続けたいの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I see… I'm sorry.\n…But right now‚ I want to continue the rehearsal.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "話は後にしてちょうだい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let's talk later‚ please.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ダメです。こころも愛もバテてるじゃないですか\nそんな状態で続けても意味がない。休憩をとりましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ it's not possible. Kokoro and Ai are exhausted.\nIt's meaningless to continue in that state. Let's take a break.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "……何言ってるの。知ってるでしょ？\n来週には今年最初のライブバトルがあるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…What are you saying? You know‚ right?\nWe have the first live battle of the year next week.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "相手は、私達の古巣……バンプロのグループよ\n今売り出し中らしいけど……絶対に負けたくない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The opponent is our former agency… Van Pro's group.\nThey're apparently in the middle of a debut now…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "今年こそLizNoirがトップを獲るためにも\nここで確実に勝っておきたいの。それに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I definitely don't want to lose.\nThis year‚ LizNoir must reach the top‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "今度のステージは、あの時と――\nNEXT VENUSグランプリと同じ会場よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "so I want to win here without fail. And…\nThe stage is the same venue as the NEXT VENUS Grand Prix.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "今度こそ勝ちたいの……あのステージで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to win this time… on that stage.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（あの場所では、いろんなことがあった……）\n（莉央さんなりに、思うところがあるんだろう）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（That place… many things happened there…）\n（Rio-san must have her own thoughts about it.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "気持ちは分かるけど、怪我をしたら元も子もありません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand your feelings‚ but if you get injured‚ it will be a setback.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "この程度で怪我をするほど、私達はヤワじゃないわ！\n――さあみんな、立って続きよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We're not so fragile that we'll get injured from something like this!\nNow everyone‚ stand up and continue!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（今日はいつもの莉央さんらしくないな。……よし）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（She's not acting like her usual self today… Alright.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01-rio012.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ、さあ、曲を流して――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa‚ haa‚ now play the music――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、莉央さん、待って。急ぎの話があるんです\n来週のライブのことで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ Rio-san‚ wait. I have something urgent to discuss.\nIt's about next week's live performance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01-rio013.m4a",
      "text": "……後じゃダメなの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Can't it wait?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "はい、今すぐにです！\nリーダーの莉央さんと話し合いが必要なんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ it's right now!\nI need to have a discussion with Leader Rio-san!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01-rio014.m4a",
      "text": "な、何よ……はぁ、分かったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-What… haa‚ fine.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "他のみんなは、少し休憩しててくれ\n水分もしっかりとってくれよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone else‚ take a short break.\nMake sure to hydrate properly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01-rio015.m4a",
      "text": "早く行くわよ。時間がもったいないんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let's go quickly. Time is precious.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 132.8
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 132.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01-rio016.m4a",
      "text": "――で、話というのは何？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ what is it that you want to talk about?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 136.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、その前に、はいこれどうぞ\n莉央さんも水分をとって。あそこの椅子に座って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ before that‚ here‚ please have this.\nRio-san‚ you should also hydrate. Sit on that chair over there…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 144.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01-rio017.m4a",
      "text": "……話があるというのは、やっぱり嘘ね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…So‚ you are lying.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 149.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "バレちゃいましたか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Did you figure it out?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 156.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01-rio018.m4a",
      "text": "私達を休ませるために、わざとこんなことを……\nまったく、貴方も食えない人になってきたわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You intentionally did this to make us rest…\nHonestly‚ you've become quite a sneaky person.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 163.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01-rio019.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと三枝さんっぽいかも\n……もちろん嫌な意味でよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's a bit like Saegusa-san.\n…But definitely not in a good way.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 165.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "すみません。でもさっきは空気がギスギスしていました\n気分を変えた方がいいと思って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry. But the atmosphere earlier was getting tense.\nI thought it would be better to change the mood.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 173.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01-rio020.m4a",
      "text": "……ギスギス、そう見えた……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Tense‚ is that how it looked…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 173.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、以前の莉央さんを思い出しました\nこの前の、NEXT VENUSグランプリの頃の",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ it reminded me of the previous Rio-san.\nThe time of the previous NEXT VENUS Grand Prix.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 180.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 184.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01-rio021.m4a",
      "text": "……私は、もうあの頃の私じゃないわ\n後輩も出来たし、海外でだって結果を出した……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I am not the same person I was back then.\nI have juniors now‚ and I've achieved results even overseas…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 189.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01-rio022.m4a",
      "text": "成長したと思ってる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I believe I have grown.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 193.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 195.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん、していますよ、誰が見ても",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ I believe that too‚ and anyone can see it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 195.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 198.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01-rio023.m4a",
      "text": "……頭では分かっているけど……\nでも、不安なのよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I know it in my head‚ but…\nI still feel anxious…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 201.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 204.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01-rio024.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……。だから、熱くなると、つい\n大人げない自分が出てきちゃうのよね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa… That's why‚ when I get heated up‚ I end up\nshowing my immature side…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 209.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 212.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "情熱があるのはいいことですよ\nいや、莉央さんは情熱がなければ、ダメです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Having passion is a good thing.\nNo‚ Rio-san‚ without passion‚ you wouldn't be the same.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 214.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 218.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01-rio025.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう。でも、グループのリーダーは\n同時に冷静さも持ってないといけないのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you. But as the leader of the group‚\nI also need to have composure.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 222.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 231.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01-rio026.m4a",
      "text": "私は周囲に助けられてばっかりよ。今だって……\nいいのかしら、私がリーダーで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've always been helped by those around me. Even now…\nIs it okay for me to be the leader?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 231.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 234.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さんが、リーダーに向いてないとは\n俺は思ってません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't think Rio-san is unsuitable to be a leader.\nThat's what I believe.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 236.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01-rio027.m4a",
      "text": "……そうかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Is that so?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 238.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 240.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_01-rio028.m4a",
      "text": "……ねぇ、この後、少し時間取れない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Hey‚ can we take some time later after this?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 240.6,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
